latestIgtvVideos.title: How to select the shade of foundation ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
There are 2 steps: 
▪️selecting the undertone 
▪️selecting the surface tone 

Surface tones are countless and undertones are three in number. 

For surface tone: choose 4 shades, apply swatches on jawline and choose the closest shade. 

For undertone: 
🔺See the colour of the veins of wrist 
  If green- warm undertone 
  If blue- cool undertone 
🔺If you’re getting tanned in the sun- warm 
  If you’re turning red in the sun- cool 

NC- warm (yellow) 
NW-cool (pink) 
N- neutral 

There are no fixed rules for makeup. It’s all about playing up. If you have a shade darker or lighter, you can mix 2 foundations and apply♥️
